  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Examine the construct validity, the group discriminant ability, and the inter-rater
      reliability of a novel dementia rating scale (QuQu scale: QUick QUestion scale) candidate for
      the evaluation of patients with Alzheimer Dementia (AD)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
